### 1. 注册用户
POST http://192.168.52.143:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "student",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "email": "test@qq.com",
  "role": "user",
  "status": 1,
  "remark": "注册测试"
}

### 2. 登录 → 自动获取 token
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "student",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### 3. 景区列表
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/spot/list
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 景区详情（id=1 青城山）
GET http://localhost:8080/spot/detail?id=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 景区名称下拉列表
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/spot/nameList
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

----------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. 查询【所有酒店】（无任何参数）
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/hotel/list
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 按【酒店名称模糊查询】（例：查“青城”相关酒店）
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/hotel/list?hotelName=青城
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 按【星级筛选】（例：5星酒店）
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/hotel/list?starLevel=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 按【景区名字查询】
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/hotel/list?scenicName=成都青城山
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 【名称 + 星级】组合查询（例：含“温泉”的4星酒店）
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/hotel/list?hotelName=温泉&starLevel=4
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### 查询特定酒店详细
GET http://192.168.52.155:8080/hotel/detail?id=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

